  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1222">
<l>puṉkaṇṇai vāḻi maruṇmālai eṅkēḷpōl </l>
<l> vaṉkaṇṇa tōniṉ ṟuṇai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A long life to you, O dark evening! You are sightless. Is your help-mate (also) as hard-hearted as mine.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
